  ## Description

  Used to store in the session a key and its value.

  ## Syntax

      {% raw %}{% session_assign <key> = <value> %}{% endraw %}

  ## Example

      {% raw %}{% session_assign email = 'john@doe.net' %}
      E-mail: {{ session.email }}{% endraw %}

